title: Worlds Missions
body: Ive got one mission showing saying complete 6 more missions but there arent any other missions...... ??

replies.body: This time the mission comes/updates weekly. So "complete X more mission" is gonna take a while.
More free missions are out on October 2nd :D
Do you know where they said Oct 2nd? I figured it would be out by now (7pm AEST) if it was still the 2nd :'(
[It's probably American time](https://twitter.com/moobeat/status/913582466782425088), I forgot to convert. MB
